  "texts": [
    "Additionally, Data Mining (DM) techniques help identify learning patterns, behavioral trends, and knowledge gaps, facilitating personalized learning environments [31,32].To improve engagement, EduLLMs integrate multimodal technologies, such as:• Computer Vision (CV): Analyzing students' facial expressions and body language for real-time feedback [42].• Voice Recognition: Supporting oral practice, speech evaluation, and pronunciation correction in language learning environments [33].These technologies allow EduLLMs to provide a flexible, real-time learning experience tailored to individual student needs.",
    "Chatbots and intelligent tutoring systems powered by LLMs offer 24/7 personalized assistance, reducing educators' workload and enhancing learning efficiency [34][35][36].However, challenges persist regarding the ethical deployment of LLMs in education.",
    "Issues like data bias, student privacy, and algorithm transparency must be addressed to ensure equitable and inclusive learning experiences [9,37,38].",
    "Evolution of LLMsThe evolution of LLMs demonstrates their increasing capacity to handle complex NLP tasks.",
    "Early models like GPT-1 showed flexibility in tasks such as language translation, sentiment analysis, and text categorization [3].The release of GPT-2 marked a turning point, as it introduced significant enhancements over GPT-1."
